These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, october, november
House: wooden, cottage, palace, futuristic
1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
2. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
3. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
5. the wooden house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday      | november  | september | january  | october |
| House   | palace | futuristic      | wooden | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, daffodil, dahlia
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pumpkin, apricot, kiwi
1. the person who growsmarigold is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower   | dahlia | daffodil | marigold   | sunflower |
| Food           | apricot      | blueberry    | pumpkin | kiwi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, basketball, soccer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, january, february
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Sport        | lacrosse | golf | basketball     | soccer |
| Birthday   | november  | february   | january | june    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, electrician, pilot, coach
City: edinburgh, hamburg, london, liverpool
1. the scientist is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the coach is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
3. the scientist is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to hamburg##2
4. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | pilot | scientist | electrician | coach |
| City   | liverpool   | london     | hamburg    | edinburgh       |

