.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, blend, chaman
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, july, october
1. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
3. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Cigar          | blend | chaman   | bolivar   | bluemaster    |
| Birthday   | september  | october | november | july |

