.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, volleyball, ice-hockey
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, woodworking, gardening
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Sport           | golf | weightlifting | ice-hockey | volleyball |
| Hobby   | woodworking        | gardening     | drawing       | hiking   |

