.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, manager, dancer
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, thai, japanese, egyptian
1. the thai is the dancer##1
2. the bartender is between the fisherman and the japanese##2
3. the indonesian is in an even position##4
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
5. the bartender is in an even position##4
6. the manager is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | fisherman | bartender  | manager  | dancer   |
| Nationality           | egyptian  | indonesian | japanese | thai |

