.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, juice, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, punk, salsa, gospel
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | cola | juice     | coffee   |
| Music-Genre    | gospel | punk  | salsa | house |

