.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, entrepreneur, dancer, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the dancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the software-developer is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Job   | software-developer | dancer | mechanic   | entrepreneur |
| Transport       | ship       | jet-ski   | boat | car |

