.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, dutch, spanish
There 4 different types of food: onion, lettuce, artichoke, broccoli
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
2. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
3. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
5. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | dutch       | mexican   | spanish        |
| Food      | lettuce  | broccoli | onion | artichoke |

