.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, animation, thriller, adventure
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, orange, azure, ebony
1. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
2. the person who likes azure is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
5. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
6. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
7. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | action | animation   | thriller | adventure     |
| Color   | orange     | grey | azure  | ebony |

