.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, go, canasta
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, rabbit, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
4. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Game   | scrabble | go        | canasta        | bridge |
| Pet         | rabbit  | bird | hamster | chinchilla |

