1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | woodworking | sudoku | puzzles |
| Birthday   | may | december | october   | june  |

