4. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
