.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, january, september
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, billiard, domino
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | april   | january  | december      | september       |
| Game   | billiard | domino | bridge | mah-jongg |

