3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
