The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, boat, airplane, bike
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Sport      | rugby     | volleyball | parkour     | rowing |
| Transport   | airplane | bike  | motorbike | boat        |

