.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, iced-tea, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, musical, fantasy
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
6. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking coffee and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage        | juice     | coffee | tea | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | fantasy | mystery      | martial-arts        |

 